  h5.strong Forming Methods
  .annotate I though I'd explain how the forming methods works using numbered poker chips to draw the teams. Each player has a Raw Quota, or the decimal value of what their quota would be without any rounding or truncation. The players for the event are sorted (seeded) by this number. 

  h5.strong Seeded
